b>active</b>: true</p><p><b>patient</b>: <a href=\"Patient-example0.html\">Stella Franklin (official) Female, DoB: 1985-10-14 ( IHI: Austalian Healthcare Identifier - Individual#8003608833357361)</a></p><p><b>relationship</b>: <span title=\"Codes:{http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v2-0131 N}, {http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-RoleCode FAMMEMB}\">Next-of-Kin</span></p><p><b>name</b>: Alex Baker </p><p><b>telecom</b>: ph: (02) 5550 6767</p><p><b>gender</b>: Other</p></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
